      "rationale": "The validation activity replicates the COU geometry (non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw), loading mode (ASTM F1717 static compression-bending), and material lot. The only deviation from the COU is the single test condition (see Test conditions factor). Overall, the validation activities are judged directly relevant to the COU."
